text: Villa del Rosario is the name of several places: * Villa del Rosario, Córdoba, Argentina * Villa del Rosario, Entre Ríos, Argentina * Villa del Rosario, the former name of present-day Rosario, Santa Fe, Argentina * Villa del Rosario, Norte de Santander, Colombia * Villa del Rosario, Paraguay, San Pedro, Paraguay * Villa del Rosario, Uruguay, village in Lavalleja Department, Uruguay * La Villa del Rosario, Venezuela
title: Villa del Rosario
